              <tr> 
                <td class="chblue"><font class="h1font"> Intermediate Decks</font></td></tr></table></td></tr><tr><td><table width="100%" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="3"><tr><td><font class="bfont"><table width="100%" border="0" cellpadding="4" cellspacing="0"><tr><td colspan="2"><font class="h1font">Bring the Toast: Bread and Butter</font></td></tr><TR><TD WIDTH="10%" VALIGN="TOP"><font class="h2font"> Rating</Font></TD><TD><img src="/magination/gfx/star3.gif" width="21" height="22" border="0" align="absmiddle"><img src="/magination/gfx/star3.gif" width="21" height="22" border="0" align="absmiddle"><img src="/magination/gfx/star3.gif" width="21" height="22" border="0" align="absmiddle"><img src="/magination/gfx/star3.gif" width="21" height="22" border="0" align="absmiddle"><font size=1>(4.45)</font> | <A HREF="/magination/decks/decks.php?reviews=21947">Read Reviews</A></TD></TR><TR><TD WIDTH="10%" VALIGN="TOP"><font class="h2font"> Author</font></TD><TD><font class="bfont"> <A HREF="http://www.decktech.net/magination/main/mpage.php?member=9634">Lee "Perfect Saru" Marino</A></FONT> <font class="afont"> <a href='http://www.decktech.net/magination/main/mpage.php?member=9634&sub=1'> (Subscribe to this member)</a></font></TD></TR><TR><TD WIDTH="10%" VALIGN="TOP"><font class="h2font"> Description</Font></TD><TD> </TD></TR><TR><TD COLSPAN="2" VALIGN="TOP"><font class="bfont"> Old skool playstyle, deck with incredible focus. Uses speed as greatest advantage.</FONT></TD></TR><TR><TD WIDTH="10%" VALIGN="TOP"><font class="h2font"> Submitted</Font></TD><TD><font class="bfont"> March 6, 2002</FONT></TD></TR><TR><TD WIDTH="10%" VALIGN="TOP"><font class="h2font"> Cards</Font></TD><TD> </TD></TR><TR><TD COLSPAN="2" VALIGN="TOP"><font class="bfont"> magi:<br>
<a href="javascript:card_browser(376)">Barak</a><br>
(Starting: <a href="javascript:card_browser(369)">Lava <a href="javascript:card_browser(395)">Balamant</a></a>, <a href="javascript:card_browser(359)">Arbolit</a>, <a href="javascript:card_browser(393)">Thermal Blast</a>)<br>
<a href="javascript:card_browser(381)">Valkan</a><br>
(Starting: <a href="javascript:card_browser(371)">Quor</a>, <a href="javascript:card_browser(359)">Arbolit</a>)<br>
<a href="javascript:card_browser(677)">Vorga</a><br>
(Starting: <a href="javascript:card_browser(359)">Arbolit</a>, <a href="javascript:card_browser(386)">Scroll of Fire</a>)<br>
<br>
Creatures:<br>
<a href="javascript:card_browser(359)">Arbolit</a> x1<br>
<a href="javascript:card_browser(672}<a href="javascript:card_browser({516)">Gia</a>nt <a href="javascript:card_browser(394)">Arboll</a></a> x3<br>
<a href="javascript:card_browser(371)">Quor</a> x2<br>
<a href="javascript:card_browser(361)">Drakan</a> x3<br>
